    <h3>Step 1: Learn</h3>
    <p class="summary">Get the facts about composting&hellip;</p>
    <div class="action--description">
      <p>Over 36 million tons of food waste reach landfills each year in the United States. This waste could be composted to be reused for richer soil.</p>
      <p>Adding compost to soil reduces the need to use fertilizers - better for the environment and your health!</p>
